The Green Green Grass has received fairly good viewing audiences since its debut in 2005. Attracting around five to six million viewers per episode it provides competition for other mainstream sitcoms such as ''[[My Family]]'' and ''[[Gavin and Stacey]]''. The sitcom however has not been nominated for any awards even though it has a large following.
